vertiser Co.|location=Honolulu|edition=2}}\n* {{Citation |ref=harv|first= Heber J. |last= Grant |title= [[Teachings of Presidents of the Church: Heber J. Grant]] |chapter= The Life and Ministry of Heber J. Grant |chapterurl= https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/manual/teachings-heber-j-grant/the-life-and-ministry-of-heber-j-grant?lang=eng |year= 2002 |publisher= LDS Church |lccn= 2004268057 |oclc= 54500103 }}\n* {{citation |ref=harv|url= https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/article/groundbreaking-sapporo-japan-temple |title= Groundbreaking Held For Sapporo Japan Temple |type= News Release |work= MormonNewsroom.org |publisher= LDS Church |date= October 22, 2011 |accessdate= 2014-10-15 }}\n* {{citation |ref=harv|first= Gordon B. |last= Hinckley |authorlink= Gordon B. Hinckley |date= March 1964 |title= The Church in the Orient |url= https://archive.org/stream/improvementera6703unse#page/n23/mode/2up |journal= [[Improvement Era]] |volume= 67 |issue= 3 |pages= 166\u2013193 }}\n* {{Citation|ref={{harvid|Mormon Newsroom}}|title=History of the Church in Japan|url=https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/article/history-of-the-church-in-japan|accessdate=22 March 2018|work=Mormon Newsroom|publisher=The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints}}\n* {{citation |ref=harv|last1=Hoffman|first1=John P.|title=Japanese Saints: Mormons in the land of the rising sun|date=2007|publisher=Lexington Books|location=Lanham, MD|isbn=978-0-7391-1689-0}}\n*{{citation|ref=harv|last1=Josephson |first1=Jason Ananda |date=2012|title=The Invention of Religion in Japan |url=http://press.uchicago.edu/ucp/books/book/chicago/I/bo13657764.html |website=The University of Chicago Press Books |publisher=University of Chicago Press |accessdate=7 June 2018}}\n* {{citation |ref={{harvid|Deseret News, 1970a}}|title= LDS Display Draws Throngs at Expo '70 |url= https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=odAiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=aEoDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2454%2C3169312 |newspaper= Deseret News |date= March 16, 1970 |pages= B1, B2 }}\n* {{Citation|ref={{harvid|The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints Meetinghouse Locator}}|title=Meetinghouse Locator|url=https://www.lds.org/maps/meetinghouses/@35.340770,135.137519,6&id=:::::Japan:33.211116,138.383789|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180323031539/https://www.lds.org/maps/meetinghouses/@35.340770,135.137519,6&id=:::::Japan:33.211116,138.383789|url-status=dead|archive-date=23 March 2018|website=The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints|publisher=The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints|accessdate=22 March 2018}}\n* {{citation |ref=harv|last1=Mori|first1=Komae|last2=Harris|first2=David W.|title=The Other Side of the Rising Sun: Tatsui Sato and the growth of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints in Japan|date=2005|publisher=Granite Publishing and Distribution|location=Orem, UT|isbn=1-59936-004-7}}\n*{{citation|ref={{harvid|Desert Sun|1970}}|title=Mormon Pavilion|url=https://cdnc.ucr.edu/cgi-bin/cdnc?a=d&d=DS19700227.2.118|accessdate=26 April 2018|agency=Desert Sun|issue=176|publisher=California Digital Newspaper Collection|date=27 February 1970}}\n* {{Citation|ref=harv|editor1-last=Neilson|editor1-first=Reid L.|editor2-last=Gessel|editor2-first=Van C.|title=Taking the Gospel to the Japanese 1901 to 2001|date=2006|publisher=Brigham Young University|location=Provo, UT|isbn=0-8425-2595-5}}\n* {{citation |ref={{harvid|LDS Church News, 2013}}|url= https://www.thechurchnews.com/archive/2013-03-05/new-mission-presidents-by-area-for-2013-39276 |title= New mission presidents by area for 2013 |date= March 5, 2013 |newspaper= [[LDS Church News]] |accessdate= 2014-10-05 }}\n* {{citation |ref={{harvid|Deseret News, 2009}}|title= President Thomas S. Monson: 'Welcome to Conference' |url= http://www.deseretnews.com/article/705334254/President-Thomas-S-Monson-Welcome-to-Conference.html |newspaper= [[Deseret News]] |date= October 3, 2009 |accessdate= 2012-11-06 }}\n* {{Citation|ref=harv|last1=Renouard|first1=Chelynne|tit